			<article id="post-780" class="post-780 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-energy-oil-gas tag-brookings-rockefeller-project-on-state-and-metropolitan-innovation tag-cefia tag-clean-energy tag-clean-energy-finance-and-investment-authority tag-export-import-bank-of-the-united-states tag-green-banks tag-new-energy-economy tag-overseas-private-investment-corporation tag-regional-greenhouse-gas-initiative">

